reviewText: My daughter found this for our family to watch on a trip. It was what I expected from a made for TV movie and was enjoyed by all
Very good! I love Brooke White...I was rooting for her on American idol,I was sorry she got voted off!!!
I bought this as a gift. I heard that they loved it and was a great add on to their DVD's.
This is a clean, cute family movie....We loved it!!!  We originally weren't going to buy it then gave in and did so and were pleasantly surprised...and happy that we did!!!
Realistically cast actors who provided a great situation type drama. Good for the whole family. Enjoyed seeing Brooke White on the big screen and hearing her sing again. Worth repeat watching.
This was a very well done movie with a powerful message. Illustrates that our plans are not always His plans for our lives.
